snippet.title: Galaxy Trader - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hforsyth.galaxytrader

Now available on PC: https://hf-games.itch.io/galaxy-trader

Galaxy Trader is a relaxing, open world space RPG. You'll enjoy it if you're looking for a peaceful exploration game that focuses on cargo hauling and trading.

Made with ❤️ by one person!
